messages.content: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.
Ask Fredrik Thordendal How's the new album coming along.
Sure—what phone number should I use to send Fredrik Thordendal the message?
I don’t have his phone number.
I can send that for you—could you please provide Fredrik Thordendal’s phone number (or contact ID) so I know where to send the message?
I really have no idea what his phone number or contact ID is.

I’ll need a way to reach Fredrik—either his phone number or a contact ID from your address book. Do you have any of those details, or would you like me to help you search your contacts/messages for “Fredrik Thordendal”?
I honestly don't have any of that info. Could you try finding it yourself?

I’m not finding any existing contact or message for Fredrik Thordendal, so I don’t have a phone number or contact ID on file. I’ll need that information to send your message. Let me know if you’re able to locate his number or contact details!
